4mKaoEPTVTG9WcU5ErTKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=ef1cba0c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.patreon.com/posts/jing-ji-xue-yu-37807348</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T07:47:21.000Z","msg":"我諗係得香港先比較多人停係 右翼=資本主義、左翼＝共產主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾十年前左右翼已經唔再係資本主義vs共產主義 <br />\n而係新自由主義(右)vs社會民主主義(左)<br />\n而西歐北歐行社會民主主義已經好多年<br />\n詳細:<br />\n社會民主主義<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Social_democracy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FSocial_democracy&d=OUx24mKaoEPTVTG9WcU5ErTKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=96cb921e\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Social_democracy</a><br />\n新自由主義<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Neoliberalism\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FNeoliberalism&d=OUx24mKaoEPTVTG9WcU5ErTKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=3a91847d\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Neoliberalism</a>"},{"pid":"24ee0c770a1577e2f22cb3441f79f70e74449295","tid":2051961,"uid":17696,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T07:54:43.000Z","msg":"比人成日吹奏既社會民主主義令瑞典係70年代破產克朗貶值30%<br />\n救返瑞典經濟既係瑞典再次行返資本主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48e0c9a811d8c91bcc41a1701125c4ac297e9bd9","tid":2051961,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T08:01:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"357cd2a6520965675aa14ad5748a0626a761cc89","tid":2051961,"uid":265582,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"24ee0c770a1577e2f22cb3441f79f70e74449295","tid":2051961,"uid":17696,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T07:54:43.000Z","msg":"比人成日吹奏既社會民主主義令瑞典係70年代破產克朗貶值30%<b